        <h2>Overview</h2>
        <p>Our client in Detroit is seeking an in-house Sr. Creative Director to join their team!</p>
        <p>This position is responsible for providing strategic brand and creative leadership on all content and
            execution, including packaging, digital and traditional advertising, website product and brand content,
            brand creative expression, and sales enablement materials. It also includes direct management of the
            creative resources across the organization, talent development, and overall creative capabilities of the
            company. It works with cross functional partners and stakeholders to ensure creative needs are being
            delivered with quality including working with the senior manager of creative operations, the head of
            ecommerce, and the head of marketing communications.</p>

        <h2>Roles & responsibilities</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><span class="p--body-emphasis">Adaptable and able to work under pressure –</span> is flexible, maintains
                effectiveness by adjusting behavior, work routines, and habits to meet a goal and/or changing
                circumstances. Is seen as balanced despite the conflicting demands of the situation</li>
            <li><span class="p--body-emphasis">Building collaborative relationships –</span> ability to establish
                credibility and develop, maintain, and strengthen partnerships with others inside and outside the
                organization</li>
            <li><span class="p--body-emphasis">External resource management –</span> ability to manage agency partners
                and contractors to meet design and quality standards, deadlines, and budget requirements</li>
        </ul>
