            blank] years ago?”</p>

        <h2>Education & experience</h2>
        <ul>
            <li>Bachelor’s degree in Marketing, Communications, Graphic Design, or equivalent experience</li>
            <li>10+ years of work experience in a creative, brand development, design or related marketing roles</li>
            <li>10+ years brand development; comfortable with creating brand identities from the ground up</li>
            <li>5+ years in graphic design with a strong digital portfolio</li>
            <li>5+ years in art direction or creative role for websites and ecommerce</li>
            <li>5+ years responsive email design experience</li>
        </ul>


